# Parser Error Codes

All parser error codes MUST be defined in `lib/parser/errors.ts` inside `PARSER_ERRORS`.

```typescript
// ✅ Correct
import { PARSER_ERRORS } from "@/lib/parser/errors";
code: PARSER_ERRORS.MISSING_CLAVE_ACCESO

// ❌ Wrong - inline string
code: "MISSING_CLAVE_ACCESO"
```

When adding new errors: add to `PARSER_ERRORS`, then import and use.
